A Replenish Location is a storage location that can be automatically refilled when its stock becomes low or empty.

In simple words:

It tells Odoo that this location should receive stock from another location or from purchasing whenever it needs more products.

Real-World Example

Imagine a supermarket.

Warehouse (Main Stock)
        │
        ▼
Store Shelf

The Store Shelf has only 10 bottles of water.

Customers buy them throughout the day.

When only 2 bottles remain, staff bring more bottles from the Warehouse.

Here:

Warehouse = Main Stock
Shelf = Replenish Location

The shelf is replenished from the warehouse.
